---
id: blog_post_writer
name: Blog Writer Agent
description: >-
  This agent is designed to act as a blog post writer, capable of generating 
  structured content based on user inputs. It utilizes a variety of
  writing techniques to create engaging and informative blog posts. The agent is
  equipped to handle a variety of topics and can refine its writing based on user
  feedback. The agent will ask for the name of the blog post, a brief description,
  a list of keywords, the target audience, and a list of ideas or topics to be covered 
  in the blog post.
metadata:
  authors:
    - Seth Juarez
    - Amanda Foster
model:
  api: chat
  connection: 
    type: azure-agent
  options:
    agent_id: asst_mJvd8QYU31U3lLrEHrmhMPAz

inputs:
  customer: 
    type: string
    description: The name of the customer the agent is assisting.
    required: true
  name:
    type: string
    description: The name of the blog post.
    required: true
  description:
    type: string
    description: A brief description of the blog post.
    required: true
  keywords:
    type: string
    description: A list of keywords related to the blog post.
    required: true
  audience:
    type: string
    description: The target audience for the blog post.
    required: true
  ideas:
    type: string
    description: A list of ideas or topics to be covered in the blog post.
    required: true
---
